## 1. Dataset Overview

### 1.1 Dataset Name
Satellite Telemetry Dataset for Anomaly Detection (STAD)

### 1.2 Purpose
This dataset provides telemetry time-series data for training and validating unsupervised anomaly detection models in satellite operations context.

### 1.3 Dataset Type
- [ ] Real satellite telemetry (if available)
- [x] Simulated/synthetic telemetry
- [ ] Copernicus Sentinel-1/2 tiles
