- **Sampling Rate:** [e.g., 1 Hz, 0.1 Hz]
- **Total Samples:** [TBD]
- **Total Duration:** [TBD]
- **Timestamp Format:** ISO 8601 (UTC)

**Telemetry Parameters (Example):**
| Parameter | Unit | Range | Sampling Rate | Description |
|-----------|------|-------|---------------|-------------|
| Battery Voltage | V | 20-35 | 1 Hz | Main battery voltage |
| Solar Array Current | A | 0-10 | 1 Hz | Solar panel output current |
| Temperature_CPU | °C | -20 to 60 | 0.5 Hz | Onboard computer temperature |
| Temperature_Battery | °C | -10 to 40 | 0.5 Hz | Battery pack temperature |
| Attitude_Roll | deg | -180 to 180 | 10 Hz | Spacecraft roll angle |
| Attitude_Pitch | deg | -90 to 90 | 10 Hz | Spacecraft pitch angle |
| Attitude_Yaw | deg | -180 to 180 | 10 Hz | Spacecraft yaw angle |
| Communication_SNR | dB | 0-40 | 0.1 Hz | Signal-to-noise ratio |

