### 9.3 Data Loading Example
```python
import pandas as pd

# Load telemetry data
df = pd.read_csv('data/raw/telemetry_data.csv', parse_dates=['timestamp'])
df.set_index('timestamp', inplace=True)

# Basic statistics
print(df.describe())
print(f"Date range: {df.index.min()} to {df.index.max()}")
print(f"Total samples: {len(df)}")
```

